text.tspan: Based on the assessments and index by Polity 5 (2021). It captures the extent to which open, multi-party, and
competitive elections choose a chief executive who faces comprehensive institutional constraints, and political
participation is competitive. It here ranges from 0 to 20 (fully democratic).
